title: Your account has transferred to another region. Please try logging into the appropriate region
body: i got this message today and i am really confused. my Lol account was ok 2 days ago then this happened. What do i do T_T.

replies.body:
You triple checked you entered the right details?

[You should immediately send in a ticket to Riot about it.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201751694) It may have been stolen.
